{"tid":44281,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗手術緊問","createTime":"2016-12-18T07:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T07:02:49.000Z","uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a41fc6980c69bd8152cd8735178e8c146ded23","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"因為先天問題，隻狗仔四歲就有問題，依家住緊醫院，但係救翻都淨係可以生存一兩年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想幫佢換腎，我人生中得返佢一個屋企人 ，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想救翻佢，香港有冇得換？如果返大陸又有冇得換？價錢同過程係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106265263a1984c378d8f97ee3a10a35e3229f17","tid":44281,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"加油  但有時有啲野只可以飲恨接受<br />\n點都好 祝狗狗冇事"},{"pid":"bdab507a9a71c5a0cd2f049f60d76f897eca26bc","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"求幫忙，返大陸換腎可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我得番佢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然我仲係個學生， 但係幾多錢我都會比，佢得返一兩年命，我用依兩年做part-time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451bdf54a54f78ccf6a56324c7ea91eb1e008984","tid":44281,"uid":61628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"雖然幫唔到你手 但加油"},{"pid":"85f78c6f16008fbb56a2714c0a8aaa833f5dc417","tid":44281,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:12:41.000Z","msg":"係大陸有錢實有人做，但係用另一隻狗條命去換你隻狗條命，又係咪好事啦？最怕做完佢都係康復唔到<br />\n<br />\n我都有養狗，換著我係你可能我都做唔到咁理性嘅決定"},{"pid":"40af5980eabdf2eb2105e7e0c4c51a6a92a29371","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"我得番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我冇哂屋企人啦，女朋友又走咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe51f1ae508dd300799fb9688f5129d1ac3e5d7","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"有冇方法可以救佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a0afaf7da6e54e86098198991abee934a5ea8f","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5ffb932eb52ed66ba71e0a8e4da5c13d221cb0e2","tid":44281,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"命運，有時講就講得2年..可能會更長或更短.."},{"pid":"de5bd624ede224413af9d6c84e03f88ff98c8a8d","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>命運，有時講就講得2年..可能會更長或更短..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我想係兩年內儲錢比佢做手術，但係我Google都搵唔到點樣幫佢換腎同埋幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有經驗可以同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc6fe569f024c38e76c1c3e8d56de3745ddc574","tid":44281,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:28:18.000Z","msg":"巴打生死有命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9b7619b03fed783147e93bd9a9d6052c2d9aca","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:29:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打生死有命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我寧願我死都唔想佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aaf5ab5bd5527b3575ef9ca844d0526e63b1c9","tid":44281,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打生死有命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我寧願我死都唔想佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n趁佢仲係到既日子多d陪佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff7e9ec68ec48c98ac1a5014a15e90ab707581f","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede0e40a06f436c4dfaf7f68b7fc52298b551fe9","tid":44281,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打生死有命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我寧願我死都唔想佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n趁佢仲係到既日子多d陪佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有陣時就係咁，就好似初初狗仔出世..有腸炎..就算你點做手術都救唔到..我聽過例子太多..佢係得咁多就係得咁多..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ec97ea612fa59a6dcfe48831b92340ff09a4a5","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3c4bbbe28aec9d12eb940d64dc9152e8570a2e39","tid":44281,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>命運，有時講就講得2年..可能會更長或更短..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我想係兩年內儲錢比佢做手術，但係我Google都搵唔到點樣幫佢換腎同埋幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有經驗可以同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸嘢用百度search la, 第一個search result 就有"},{"pid":"fef7f774a9c3c7850f883519d04e11a156d48282","tid":44281,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"大陸野咪制，俾咗錢可能即晚就死<br />\n人都會被人偷器官，你覺得狗唔會咩？<br />\n香港無見過，但聽唔少食黑酵母菌，白黎醇，阿嫲子油嚟改善體質。唔少肝腎病，癌症，老年狗都有食。<br />\n我自己無經驗，建議你上網揾多啲資料，問醫生意見係咪可行。<br />\n不過，俾心理準備你，食呢啲supplement 個個月使差唔多$2,000. 你睇自己能力啦！"},{"pid":"cb6b66818678da349bb2dad1f590869297b07689","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:20:13.000Z","msg":"我見大陸啲手術都要三萬幾，應該唔會好差。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac9aa28a0d630fcfcc02c0dd179bf16c6ad37e9","tid":44281,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見大陸啲手術都要三萬幾，應該唔會好差。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人哋生仔使幾萬，咪一樣偷咗個腎"},{"pid":"6abc34d39e67adf3e78ec4c101444bc4b1bb3295","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"如果有人翻過大陸，幫隻狗換過腎，可唔可以留低聯絡方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c4752314c94c50314e17afae737294177cd84a","tid":44281,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果有人翻過大陸，幫隻狗換過腎，可唔可以留低聯絡方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該冇人會有經驗<br />\n出入境你都麻煩<br />\n<br />\n我覺得你睇睇台灣有冇啦"},{"pid":"4ff10d5e678b3623231eed42d5fa7b9a37a59af7","tid":44281,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"其實有冇問過獸醫點睇<br />\n有時獸醫唔建議既話 真係寧願唔好做..做完狗狗可能仲辛苦<br />\n唔好怪我直接 我都有養貓狗 但如果佢生活得幾痛苦 你都單純想佢係自己身邊既話 呢啲叫自私<br />\n加油 有咩想講就講出黎 我會keep住睇呢個post"},{"pid":"1fa3884295fa9291f18f012b6ba228331e713204","tid":44281,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"13d953518ae62be040a84241aa2a6fed5edcef1d","tid":44281,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"714f820519c766b13044545161df449438a03566","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有冇問過獸醫點睇<br />\n有時獸醫唔建議既話 真係寧願唔好做..做完狗狗可能仲辛苦<br />\n唔好怪我直接 我都有養貓狗 但如果佢生活得幾痛苦 你都單純想佢係自己身邊既話 呢啲叫自私<br />\n加油 有咩想講就講出黎 我會keep住睇呢個post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢四歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e6bfe293655b46858f4a5b012bd9a35566db92","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果有人翻過大陸，幫隻狗換過腎，可唔可以留低聯絡方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該冇人會有經驗<br />\n出入境你都麻煩<br />\n<br />\n我覺得你睇睇台灣有冇啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣應該過100,000，我自己都頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37307298436cef5b5c6b1c0286a0f1774df7ad3","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇問過獸醫點睇<br />\n有時獸醫唔建議既話 真係寧願唔好做..做完狗狗可能仲辛苦<br />\n唔好怪我直接 我都有養貓狗 但如果佢生活得幾痛苦 你都單純想佢係自己身邊既話 呢啲叫自私<br />\n加油 有咩想講就講出黎 我會keep住睇呢個post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢四歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其得返我同佢相依為伴，我都知自己自私，但我真係想醫好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31207fbe5256259281be03ca525aa7e82f1ed2c8","tid":44281,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇問過獸醫點睇<br />\n有時獸醫唔建議既話 真係寧願唔好做..做完狗狗可能仲辛苦<br />\n唔好怪我直接 我都有養貓狗 但如果佢生活得幾痛苦 你都單純想佢係自己身邊既話 呢啲叫自私<br />\n加油 有咩想講就講出黎 我會keep住睇呢個post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢四歲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其得返我同佢相依為伴，我都知自己自私，但我真係想醫好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明，盡量等佢開心啲啦<br />\n佢要受一刀都唔易<br />\n<br />\n我都盡量每日俾主人開心啲過日子"},{"pid":"4eef7ed60e773bc8f87e92a91208e8b2abec1ab6","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:24:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人有門路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1e6ae8ad8d0f8c550a9a6c4d5bb17ffb07a0b1","tid":44281,"uid":36915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:27:19.000Z","msg":"長痛不如短痛<br />\n醫番得二至三年命<br />\n比隻狗狗安樂死先係最好"},{"pid":"7bcb9754e6c11790cd31134357da681375edd0ff","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長痛不如短痛<br />\n醫番得二至三年命<br />\n比隻狗狗安樂死先係最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我問過，佢個腎得返三成，又唔算老，而家好返只可以活多一，兩年，但係換咗腎有機會去到10幾歲。<br />\n<br />\n 我知佢捱一刀好辛苦， 但係佢仲後生，如果再遲啲就捱唔住果一刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1818802adcd9d1ef543eca283e3fb6870bb53673","tid":44281,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>長痛不如短痛<br />\n醫番得二至三年命<br />\n比隻狗狗安樂死先係最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我問過，佢個腎得返三成，又唔算老，而家好返只可以活多一，兩年，但係換咗腎有機會去到10幾歲。<br />\n<br />\n 我知佢捱一刀好辛苦， 但係佢仲後生，如果再遲啲就捱唔住果一刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放心 狗仔4歲其實已經唔係細路 等於人既廿歲 會頂到手術<br />\n但你有冇問獸醫點換？"},{"pid":"a7c9cb3f6dad6476cc27833f413ffdb6897b0a2c","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re