ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798144b8529547414650ecaaa0c0341f0cf3912c","tid":44281,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢今日都出唔到院，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢真係好痛好痛，呼吸好急速，俾隻手我都唔得，我竟然有一刻想幫佢安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻狗腎功能有幾多？"},{"pid":"be6415f68a497181866422e38e809c4861249303","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢今日都出唔到院，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢真係好痛好痛，呼吸好急速，俾隻手我都唔得，我竟然有一刻想幫佢安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻狗腎功能有幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話三成喎，而家諗住照超聲波，睇下佢有冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f3acd6ea80d1ccd3fcfd36e447cadbf7161a8e","tid":44281,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"我明你心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我諗呢度應該冇乜人會有經驗<br />\n你不如上大陸論壇睇下有冇人做過，會唔會風險好高？拎返大陸做隨時連個一兩年都冇埋呀巴打"},{"pid":"c70f9d3a01ddee7bf388bcdea810245b8983a37a","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"如果知道隻狗冇得救，你地會繼續俾佢吊鹽水定係出院同佢周圍玩下"},{"pid":"b34bf3155aa4d7d2f4023cb3d548dd22b6aac34d","tid":44281,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"如果你係唔夠錢既，連登既手足都會幫你既"},{"pid":"5f9443fe60556bbb9156f94834d033320991388e","tid":44281,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"有無問過香港個醫生有無中國既寵物醫院介紹阿？"},{"pid":"36d7f7e99e3739cf518bd6eb0afc198405e293ce","tid":44281,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無問過香港個醫生有無中國既寵物醫院介紹阿？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個醫生話香港冇寵物肝臟移植，就算我想返大陸，都要時間，例如偷渡嗰啲，我仲要短時間內咁多錢同搵醫院。佢都頂唔住啦<br />\n<br />\n原本諗住可以儲錢一年後同佢做手術，但係而家個情況應該一個禮拜就去天國，詳細仲要等佢照超聲波，睇吓究竟有得救定冇得救。<br />\n<br />\n我好怕佢一無吊鹽水就死，我唔知可以做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr